{"tid":1898721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【大家心照】鄧麗欣興奮開香檳講「煞景」引支那人不滿","createTime":"2020-02-26T08:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T08:53:35.000Z","uid":25468,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd605b41bda23d75d700737257a04feafb5eea71","tid":1898721,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/x1RodAoCfCz2nSpCMYJ1uhFOsi4=/802x1425/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DVQW54USWOSOKIWGV5XDA5FKNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fx1RodAoCfCz2nSpCMYJ1uhFOsi4%3D%2F802x1425%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDVQW54USWOSOKIWGV5XDA5FKNM.jpg&h=1a1e8fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東話，同音字很多，同一發音而聯想到的字可以有很多個，不同組合有不同意思，但一字之差，意思差天共地。<br />\n<br />\n有份角逐今屆金像獎影后的鄧麗欣（Stephy）近日在IG貼圖，她與10支相信是香檳類的物體合照，並配字說：「咁高興，係因為今日煞景」，她更落tag強調「#唔係煞科」。「煞景」，同一讀音可以變成&hellip;&hellip;（你懂的），加上香檳，可能引得一班玻璃心碎片滿地。<br />\n<br />\n可能知道自己「闖禍」，今晚Stephy在另一社交平台&mdash;&mdash;主力是使用人民幣人士才會關注的微博急急解畫說：「看見網上有不少評論的言語，所以我認為有必要解釋一下。通常劇組拍戲圓滿完成了，國語說法是『殺青』，而粵語講法則是『煞科』。就是一個重要的場景完成了我們會說『煞景』，這是從拍戲以來圈中一直的認知言語。而我絕對是一個心口如一的人，更不懂得甚麼隱喻。」<br />\n<br />\n認衰的Stephy更表示自己會反省言行：「作為一個藝人我深知言行的影響，所以感謝大家及時的提醒與批評，以後我會格外小心，如果這次造成大家誤會或感到不適，我深表歉意！希望大家不要再作太多聯想！」而Stephy另以大眾關注的武漢肺炎作post的結尾：「在這個非常時期，我明白大家心情會很低落，很沮喪，我也一直祈求不好的事盡快遠離我們。林林總總也許是生命的無常，唯愛能戰勝一切！最後期望疫情早日散去，大家注意防護！保重身體！」而她的經理人公司凱藝國際亦「加把口」幫Stephy「補鑊」，為武漢加油。<br />\n<br />\nStephy的解畫post一出，網民似乎相當受落，並指「清者自清，希望各位別過份解讀」、「放心，我們都相信你」，Stephy成功過關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/1agOGV9WJHZvFNvfy4oLl5quFn4=/802x373/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/OGG2RDM6FIB2OSRSV7I54B4DZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F1agOGV9WJHZvFNvfy4oLl5quFn4%3D%2F802x373%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FOGG2RDM6FIB2OSRSV7I54B4DZ4.jpg&h=7f680205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/FK2PH6UGCshRAjAFHKQptkAMdZY=/802x153/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XQDA3UPWJAOMS74QCHWQGQ7GBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FFK2PH6UGCshRAjAFHKQptkAMdZY%3D%2F802x153%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXQDA3UPWJAOMS74QCHWQGQ7GBQ.jpg&h=7a715a33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/qDXkzFre-pUkHP5FmZfIeghBxO4=/802x568/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SKYTTWXKK47EPCS2QCU7CDH3LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FqDXkzFre-pUkHP5FmZfIeghBxO4%3D%2F802x568%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSKYTTWXKK47EPCS2QCU7CDH3LY.jpg&h=c19d4115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200225/J23YK6G6KQTAAD72KNQP2RWJDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200225%2FJ23YK6G6KQTAAD72KNQP2RWJDI%2F&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=72042996\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200225%2FJ23YK6G6KQTAAD72KNQP2RWJDI%2F&h=5690e5eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200225/J23YK6G6KQTAAD72KNQP2RWJDI/</a>"},{"pid":"7f40f20e4eb183b03ca040a8b3830b95b8f9fcfe","tid":1898721,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">響大家研究錢唔錢的時候<br />\n特衰政府已經清算手足</span><br />\nHA 清算罷工醫護<br />\n外媒記者報